- add the file Velocity.sublime-package to ~/.config/sublime-text-3/Installed\ Packages

- add the file r2.sublime-project to your R2 root. edit it to change the path to where your R2 is installed

- restart Sublime Text

- open a .vm file (or .ssp), click view > syntax > open all with current extension as... > velocity > velocity (html)

